## Common Dart Analyzer Errors & Fixes

| Code | Issue | Fix |
|------|-------|-----|
| `unused_import` | Unused import | `dart fix --apply` |
| `unused_local_variable` | Unused variable | Remove or use `_` prefix |
| `unnecessary_null_assertion` | Unnecessary `!` | `dart fix --apply` |
| `prefer_const_constructors` | Missing const | `dart fix --apply` |
| `avoid_print` | Using print() | Replace with `Logger` class |
| `curly_braces_in_flow_control` | Missing if/else braces | Manual fix |
| `always_declare_return_types` | Missing return type | Manual fix |
| `unnecessary_this` | Unnecessary this | `dart fix --apply` |

> **Most lint warnings can be resolved with `dart fix --apply`.** Only handle items requiring manual correction directly.
